ilities our team members have accrued in various operational capacities around the world.						</p>						<p>							Touchpoint IDG has a proven history of delivering world class training and exercise support to SOF and the IC.  We specialize in the holistic training of  specific advanced skills within the SOF and IC operational spectrum. Our exercise support capabilities include scenario development, complex exercise synchronization and control, role player support and surveillance red teaming (electronic and physical).						</p>						<p>							Touchpoint IDG has offices in Fayetteville, NC and will deploy Mobile Training Teams (MTT) to meet your requirment at your location. Recently Touchpoint IDG has deployed MTTs to Savannah GA, Nashville TN, Salt Lake City UT, Baltimore MD, Crestview FL, Tampa FL, San Antonio TX, Jacksonville NC, Havelock NC, San Diego, CA and other rural and urban locations.						</p>					</div>					<div class="para col3">						<h3 class="parahead">Training Programs</h3>						<ul class="subjectlist">							<li>Physical, Technical, and Rural Surveillance</li>							<li>Counter-Surveillance and Surveillance Detection</li>							<li>Advanced Force Operations (AFO)</li>							<li>Methods of Entry</li>							<li>Hostile Environment Tradecraft Course (HETC)</li>							<li>Combatives/Singleton Survival</li>							<li>Advanced Special Operations Techniques (ASOT)</li>							<li>Sensitive Site Exploitation</li>							<li>Embassy Operations</li>							<li>Tactical Photography</li>							<li>Signature Reduction</li>							<li>Marksmanship</li>							<li>Escaping Violent Situations</li>							<li>Non-Standard Communications</li>							<li>Non-­Standard iOS/Android</li>							<li>Basic Computer Security</li>							<li>Data Forensics</li>							<li>Data Protection</li>							<li>Open Source Intelligence (OSINT)</li>							<li>Wireless Analysis Course</li>						</ul>						<div style="border-top: 1px aliceblue solid; width: 100%;"></div>						<h3 class="parahea